import React from 'react'; import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; const VisionPage = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); return (
{/* Header */}
navigate(-1)} >

About Us

{/* Vision Content */}

Our Vision

To become the global leader in project management and agile education, transforming how organizations approach learning and development. We envision a world where every professional has access to world-class training that drives innovation and success.

Global Impact

We aim to reach learners worldwide, breaking down barriers to quality education and creating opportunities for growth across all industries.

Technology-Driven Learning

Leveraging cutting-edge technology to create immersive, interactive learning experiences that adapt to individual needs and learning styles.

Community Building

Fostering a vibrant community of learners, practitioners, and thought leaders who share knowledge and drive industry advancement.

{/* Bottom Navigation */}

Home

Courses

Resources

About Us

Contact

); }; export default VisionPage;
